<p>Nota: A descricao completa do produto nao esta disponivel no HTML da pagina da loja (body_html vazio no Shopify). O conteudo descritivo e exibido exclusivamente por meio das imagens do produto.</p>`,
  "prostavex": `<!-- ============================================================
     PROSTAVEX · Descrição do produto · Vida Natural
     Mesmo padrão do Meno Care. Cole no editor HTML (<>) da descrição
     do produto no Shopify (ou seção "Custom Liquid"). Escopo: .mc-pdp.
     Botões dos kits com href="#kits" (seletor nativo do tema cuida das variantes).
============================================================ -->
<div class="mc-pdp">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"> <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin=""> <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@600;700;800&family=Mulish:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap">
</div>
<style>
    

    .mc-pdp{
      --teal:#16a6a6;
      --teal-d:#0d8c8c;
      --green:#23b16a;
      --green-d:#1a9457;
      --cta:#1db955;
      --cta-d:#159a45;
      --mint:#eaf6f1;
      --mint-2:#f3faf6;
      --purple:#7c4d9c;
      --purple-l:#9d6fbe;
      --peach:#f0a98a;
      --gold:#e6a817;
      --red:#e23b3b;
      --ink:#243230;
      --muted:#6a7873;
      --line:#e3ece7;
      --radius:16px;
      font-family:'Mulish',-apple-system,system-ui,sans-serif;
      color:var(--ink);
      line-height:1.6;
      font-size:17px;
      background:#fff;
      max-width:900px;
      margin:0 auto;
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:0 16px 48px -26px rgba(22,166,166,.4);
    }
    .mc-pdp *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    .mc-pdp h1,.mc-pdp h2{text-wrap:balance}
    .mc-pdp h1,.mc-pdp h2,.mc-pdp h3,.mc-pdp .mc-disp{
      font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-.01em;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);
    }
    .mc-pdp em{font-style:normal;color:var(--green)}
    .mc-pdp .mc-wrap{padding:42px 34px}
    @media(max-width:600px){.mc-pdp{font-size:16px}.mc-pdp .mc-wrap{padding:30px 20px}}

    .mc-pdp .mc-kicker{
      display:inline-block;font-family:'Mulish',sans-serif;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:14px;
    }
    .mc-pdp .mc-center{text-align:center}

    /* ---------- BUTTONS ---------- */
    .mc-pdp a.mc-btn,
    .mc-pdp .mc-btn{
      display:inline-flex !important;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:9px;
      background:var(--cta) !important;background-image:none !important;color:#fff !important;
      font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700 !important;font-size:16.5px;letter-spacing:.01em;
      padding:16px 34px;border-radius:50px !important;border:none !important;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none !important;
      box-shadow:0 12px 26px -12px rgba(29,185,85,.7);
      transition:transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease, background .18s ease;
    }
    .mc-pdp a.mc-btn:hover,
